Customer Service

  About Us Making Your Job Easier for 65 Years

Since 1952, Lawson Products has been helping to make customers' jobs easier by improving efficiency, productivity and overall performance. 
View our company story.
Lawson Managed Inventory: Your Lawson Representative can help you lower your total cost of operation by increasing productivity and efficiency. We start by working with you to design an organized storage system and establish a re-stocking schedule based on your usage. We are on site managing your inventory just like you would. Except now you don't have to. 
Problem-Solving People: For on-site application support and technical advice, your Lawson Representative is your single point of contact.
Products for Your Applications: Based on your budget, requirements and performance needs, your Lawson Representative will recommend assortments and products for your specific applications. This way, you'll always be using the right products for the job. With a comprehensive line of products available and the ability to source hard-to-find products, we are sure to have what you need.
Facilities
Lawson Products is located in Chicago, Illinois. We serve customers from several strategically located distribution centers in North America.
 Recent Press

    The recent and continued growth of our Company has generated the following articles in the industry trade press:
     Recruiting Trends: Differentiate from the Competition and Win Candidates’ Hearts and Minds
 Industrial Supply: Building a Better Mousetrap
 Oil + Gas Monitor: Oil and Gas Cost Savings: Time is the Most Valuable Commodity
 The Enterprisers Project: VP of IT Looks for Excellence in Business Improvement
 Industrial Distribution: Inventory Management Tips to  Boost Productivity and Profit
 Industrial Distribution: Women Cash in On Distribution Sales Careers
 Industrial Supply: New and Improved: A Revitalization and Reinvestment Program Returns MRO Distributor Lawson Products to Growth Mode
 Manufacturing Business Technology: Lean Six Sigma: The Ultimate Tool to Strengthen Your Business
 Modern Distribution Management: Lawson Products' Revitalization: Distributor Adds Salespeople, Embraces Lean Six Sigma to Grow



Distinctions
